This is an android project which integrates user's Google health 
profile and helps him do grocery shopping by scanning barcode of the product 
. The application checks ingredients of the product with the user's allergies as
mentioned on his google health profile page and tells the user if the product contains
andy allergic ingredients.

The project uses Google health API. The UI is in basic Android. This is a demo app and 
does not use the database provided by US Food Services. 

Use the readme's in the respective Eclipse directories to setup and run the project.

NOTE: For more information contact mayank519@gmail.com
